data.title: Jan Waters, Real Estate Agent
data.meta_description: Jan Waters is a Coldwell Banker Realty-Gundaker real estate agent serving Chesterfield, MO and the surrounding areas.
data.text:
Service Areas and Specialties

Member of 'Team Waters', specializing in single family homes, condominiums, investment and foreclosure properties throughout the St. Louis metropolitan area with emphasis in West St. Louis County.

Dedicated to helping our clients achieve their real estate goals, our objective is to delight every client with personalized care, professional guidance and efficient administrative services.

Our years of experience combined with the vast resources available to us, will contribute to your complete satisfaction. Put us to work for you and see what a difference we can make.

Professional Experience

Member of St Louis Association of Realtors

Member of Missouri Association of Realtors

Member of National Association of Realtors

Graduate of Realestate Institute - Coldwell Banker Gundaker

Short Sale and Foreclosure Specialist

Extensive continuing education regarding market trends and license law

Professional Education and Designations

My Education is in Marketing and Sales and I have over 30 Years of Sales, Marketing and Management Experience.
